criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. 10-40 years old;

          2. Voluntary participation, signing informed consent and obtaining the consent of family
             members of patients under 18 years old;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. history and family of neurological or psychiatric disorders;

          2. history of psychiatric disorders and family history;

          3. severe somatic diseases;

          4. taking psychotropic drugs within three months;

          5. pregnancy and lactation
